title: Send Help: I'm After Me Again
description: Send Help is a collection of poetry and prose. This book has everything from love and heartbreak to thrillers and fantasy. Send Help takes the readers on a rhythmic journey that tells stories of how being trapped in your own head can lead you to a dark place. This edgy book filled with raw emotions will take your breath away and leave you craving more.
author: W. J. Corvus
